#

Hearty Vegetable Lentil Soup

55 min
$8
280 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh ProteinLow FatGluten Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthyEasy

Description

A warm and filling soup packed with nutritious vegetables and protein-rich lentils, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • green or brown lentils: 1 cup
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • spinach or kale: 2 cups, chopped
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
